78
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,958
Let's see what's on the old tube here.

79
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:07,432
l watched some news over the weekend.
That's good enough, l guess.

80
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:13,829
